SUMMARY:Davis Breakfast with the Bunny 2026
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars and share with your friends. Davis BWB is almost here! Eventbrite tickets are going fast! And this year\, we cover the service charge! \nJoin the Easter Bunny on Saturday\, April 4th at the Davis Odd Fellows Lodge for breakfast\, a parade\, egg hunting and creative play! For $15 per person\, families will enjoy a cold breakfast at 9 am with the Easter Bunny\, including cereal\, muffins\, yogurt\, juice and fruit. At about 10 o’clock\, participants will join the Bunny for a special parade through the farmers market toward the Community Church lawn to hunt for eggs! Following the hunt\, families return to the lodge to enjoy fun activities\, including cookie decorating\, card decorating\, face painting\, guided drawings\, Play-Doh\, carnival games\, and more! \nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/breakfast-with-the-bunny-2026-tickets-1983137819603
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/davis-breakfast-with-the-bunny-2026/
LOCATION:Davis Odd Fellows
CATEGORIES:Bring the Kids,Community,Games
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Breakfast-with-the-Bunny-Flyer-26-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Davis Odd Fellows":MAILTO:larrydguenther@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
