SUMMARY:Native Tree Stewardship Work Day @ Putah Creek Parkway
DESCRIPTION:Come help Tree Davis support the City of Davis Open Space Program support existing canopy along the Putah Creek Parkway. We will be weeding\, mulching\, and removing mistletoe from native trees and species in this wildlife corridor. \nMeeting place coordinates are: 38°32’06.5″N 121°43’20.4″W. Parking is available on Mariposa Circle. The closest address is 1747 Mariposa Cir\, then walk south into the Putah Creek Parkway bikepath. Sign up at https://www.treedavis.org/event-calendar/
